<!--787 yasim 

Specs:
or  75,000 lb GENXs
or  75,000 lb Rolls-Royce Trent 1000s

Typical Cruise = 0.85 Mach / 35000 ft
Max Speed = 0.87 / 35000 ft
Wing span: 60.10m
Length: 56.7 m
